    • uiReadyAdditionalTripAccommodation

      public static AddnlTripAccommodationBuilder uiReadyAdditionalTripAccommodation()
      Creates a ui ready additional trip Accommodation builder with the following field set:
      • TripIncident - if this builder is used via the withTripAccommodation() method of a trip incident builder, then use the incident created by the builder. Otherwise create a new ui ready trip incident.
      • PropertyName - set to a unique string of the form Accommodation N where N is a unique integer
      • Address - set to a UI ready address
      Returns:
      a new trip Accommodation builder
